tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within or close to normal ranges, except for a mildly decreased total CO₂, which may suggest mild metabolic acidosis or compensated respiratory alkalosis. Renal function, glucose control, and electrolytes are stable. Clinical correlation is recommended if symptoms are present.
